<verse number="20" style="v" />He sent his word and healed them,</para>

<para style="q1">and he rescued them from their destruction.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="21" style="v" />Oh that people would praise Yahweh for his covenant faithfulness</para>

<para style="q1">and for the amazing things he has done for humanity!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="22" style="v" />Let them offer the sacrifices of thanksgiving</para>

<para style="q1">and proclaim his deeds in singing.</para>

